
Implementation:
* Viewports (with lists of objects to be rendered)
* Port to windows
* Option to reload the UI init file


Data:
* Data source
 - basic model format
 - Text loader



Layout:
* Nested layout (containers with objects)
* Anchors
* Vertical and horizontal layouts (panels)




Implement other UI components:
* Button
* Checkbox
* Textbox  (text field)
* Scrollable field for displaying text and log output
* Slider
* Arrows and lines
* Images


When layout engine and ui components have been implemented,
begin implementation of basic dialogs (in lua):
* LoadObjectFile
* FileEditor


Visual:
* Transparency


Misc.:
* Load layout from XML files
* Give windows ids
* Ensure loading of fonts works on windows

